dev.blocky.library.tixte.api

Class TixteClientBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.blocky.library.tixte.api.TixteClientBuilder

  • public class TixteClientBuilder
extends Object
    Used to create new TixteClient instances.

    A single TixteClientBuilder can be reused multiple times.
    Each call to build() creates a new TixteClient instance using the same information.
    Since:
    v1.0.0-alpha.1
    Version:
    v1.1.0
    Author:
